Build dependencies:
- CMake (2.8+)
- GCC 4.6+, make (or mingw32 on Windows)


For building BallPath project use commands shown below.

Unix
----

$ mkdir buid
$ cd build
$ cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/tmp/ballpath ..
$ make -j2
$ make install


Windows (using MinGW)
---------------------

$ mkdir buid
$ cd build
$ cmake -G "MinGW Makefiles" -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=C:/Temp/ballpath ..
$ mingw32-make -j2
$ mingw32-make install
